{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01HAHBiMBjRbNkNM8aG7hR6a","type":"tool_result","content":"# Analysis of Pyth Solana Receiver SDK Content\n\n## 1) PDA Derivation Function\n**Not present** in the provided file. No `get_price_feed_account_address` function or PDA seed constants are included in this excerpt.\n\n## 2) PriceUpdateV2 Struct & LEN Constant\n```rust\n#[account]\n#[derive(BorshSchema)]\npub struct PriceUpdateV2 {\n    pub write_authority: Pubkey,\n    pub verification_level: VerificationLevel,\n    pub price_message: PriceFeedMessage,\n    pub posted_slot: u64,\n}\n\nimpl PriceUpdateV2 {\n    pub const LEN: usize = 8 + 32 + 2 + 32 + 8 + 8 + 4 + 8 + 8 + 8 + 8 + 8;\n}\n```\n\nThe constant accounts for the discriminator and field sizes totaling 152 bytes.\n\n## 3) PriceFeedMessage Fields\nThe struct is imported from `pythnet_sdk::messages`. Within tests, it's instantiated with:\n- `feed_id: [u8; 32]`\n- `ema_conf, ema_price, price, conf, exponent, prev_publish_time, publish_time`\n\nFull field definitions aren't shown in this file.\n\n## 4) VerificationLevel Enum\n```rust\n#[derive(AnchorSerialize, AnchorDeserialize, Copy, Clone, PartialEq, BorshSchema, Debug)]\npub enum VerificationLevel {\n    Partial { num_signatures: u8 },\n    Full,\n}\n```\n\nThe enum includes a `gte()` comparison method where Full always exceeds Partial variants.\n\n## 5) Constants & Discriminators\n**Not provided** in this excerpt. No seed strings or discriminator constants are defined here."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_011rr1yfgNLixmd4MBJw5da9","session_id":"846c05db-31a6-42c7-8cfa-8e6a53a70110","uuid":"bf26d72a-ee62-43a7-b63e-868c66688a04"}
